docs {
  ## Get BLS To Execution Changes

  Get signed BLS to execution change messages known by the node but not necessarily incorporated into any block.

  ### Response (200)
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "message": {
          "validator_index": "42",
          "from_bls_pubkey": "0x93247f2209abcacf57b75a51dafae777f9dd38bc7053d1af526f220a7489a6d3a2753e5f3e8b1cfe39b56f43611df74a",
          "to_execution_address": "0xabcf8e0d4e9587369b2301d0790347320302cc09"
        },
        "signature": "0xb3a7e2c6f89a1b4d5e6f708192a3b4c5d6e7f8091a2b3c4d5e6f708192a3b4c5d6e7f8091a2b3c4d5e6f708192a3b4c5d6e7f8091a2b3c4d5e6f708192a3b4c5d6e7f8091a2b3c4d5e6f708192a3b4c5d6e7f8091a2b3c4d5e6f70819"
      }
    ]
  }
  ```
}
